Javascript is a high level programming or scripting language used to make our websites and web applications interactive

Ways to add javascript to html :-
1. Inline javascript
2. internal javascript
3. External javascript

Some pre defined functions of javascript :-
alert()
prompt()
console.log()
document.write()

variables 
containers to store data in code

variable declaration method :-
1. var
2. let
3. const

rules to write variables :-
1. variables start with letter or $ or _
2. variables include only letter,  number, _ and $
3. variables are case sensitive
4. variables cannot be reserved keyword like for, if, else, etc.


datatype
primitive - number, string, boolean, undefined, null, symbol, and bigInt
non-primitive - object, array and date

functions
block of code designed to perform a particular task.

conditional statements
if,if-else,else

